statements: SELECT * FROM vpn_performance_data ORDER BY date DESC, download_speed ASC, location
SELECT id, location, upload_speed FROM vpn_performance_data WHERE download_speed > 100
SELECT MAX(download_speed) AS max_download_speed, MIN(upload_speed) AS min_upload_speed FROM vpn_performance_data
SELECT AVG(download_speed) AS avg_download_speed, AVG(upload_speed) AS avg_upload_speed FROM vpn_performance_data GROUP BY location
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance_data WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31'
SELECT id, date, location, download_speed, upload_speed FROM vpn_performance_data WHERE download_speed > 50 AND upload_speed > 20 ORDER BY date DESC
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance_data WHERE location = 'New York' ORDER BY download_speed DESC, upload_speed ASC
SELECT id, location, download_speed FROM vpn_performance_data WHERE upload_speed BETWEEN 10 AND 30 ORDER BY id
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance_data WHERE download_speed < 100 OR upload_speed > 50 ORDER BY location ASC, date DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records, AVG(download_speed) AS avg_download_speed, AVG(upload_speed) AS avg_upload_speed FROM vpn_performance_data
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance ORDER BY date DESC, download_speed ASC
SELECT server_name, user_id FROM vpn_performance WHERE upload_speed > 100
SELECT country, total_sessions FROM vpn_usage_trends WHERE total_data_usage > 1000000
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance ORDER BY upload_speed DESC, user_id ASC
SELECT server_name, download_speed FROM vpn_performance WHERE user_id = 123
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT user_id, server_name, upload_speed FROM vpn_performance WHERE download_speed > 50 ORDER BY user_id, server_name;
SELECT server_name, download_speed, upload_speed, date FROM vpn_performance WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31' ORDER BY date DESC, server_name ASC;
SELECT country, total_sessions, total_data_usage FROM vpn_usage_trends WHERE country = 'USA' OR country = 'Canada' ORDER BY total_data_usage DESC, country;
SELECT * FROM vpn_usage_trends WHERE total_data_usage > 1000000000 ORDER BY country, total_sessions DESC;
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance;
SELECT id, location FROM vpn_performance ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT id, location, performance_score FROM vpn_performance WHERE date >= '2022-01-01' AND date <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT location, performance_score FROM vpn_performance WHERE location = 'USA' ORDER BY performance_score DESC;
SELECT user_id, vpn_server_id, COUNT(*) AS usage_count FROM vpn_usage GROUP BY user_id, vpn_server_id;
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance ORDER BY performance_score DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT date, location, performance_score FROM vpn_performance WHERE location IN ('US', 'UK') ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT user_id, vpn_server_id, COUNT(*) AS total_sessions FROM vpn_usage GROUP BY user_id, vpn_server_id HAVING total_sessions > 5;
SELECT date, SUM(total_usage) AS total_usage FROM usage_trends WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' GROUP BY date ORDER BY date;
SELECT location, AVG(performance_score) AS avg_score FROM vpn_performance GROUP BY location HAVING avg_score > 7.5 ORDER BY avg_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance;
SELECT id, speed_mbps, server_location, date FROM vpn_performance;
SELECT user_id, session_start, session_end, data_usage_mb FROM vpn_usage ORDER BY data_usage_mb DESC;
SELECT location_id, country, location_name FROM vpn_locations WHERE country='USA';
SELECT * FROM vpn_users WHERE registration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM vpn_performance WHERE speed_mbps > 100 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT MAX(speed_mbps) AS max_speed, AVG(speed_mbps) AS avg_speed FROM vpn_performance GROUP BY server_location;
SELECT location_name, country, COUNT(*) AS total_vpn_users FROM vpn_users JOIN vpn_locations ON vpn_users.location_id = vpn_locations.location_id GROUP BY location_name, country;

SELECT u.username, u.email, SUM(u.data_usage_mb) AS total_usage FROM vpn_users u JOIN vpn_usage u2 ON u.user_id = u2.user_id WHERE u2.session_start BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' GROUP BY u.username, u.email;

SELECT location_name, AVG(speed_mbps) AS avg_speed FROM vpn_performance JOIN vpn_locations ON vpn_performance.server_location = vpn_locations.location_name GROUP BY location_name ORDER BY avg_speed DESC;
SELECT * FROM vpn_users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM vpn_users WHERE join_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT server_name, location, capacity FROM vpn_servers ORDER BY capacity DESC;
SELECT user_id, connection_id, usage_date, data_transferred FROM vpn_usage WHERE data_transferred > 1000;
SELECT connection_id, latency_ms, throughput_mbps FROM vpn_performance WHERE latency_ms < 50;
SELECT * FROM vpn_users WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT user_id, username, email, join_date FROM vpn_users WHERE join_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT server_name, location, capacity FROM vpn_servers ORDER BY server_name DESC;
SELECT u.username, c.connected_at, p.latency_ms FROM vpn_users u JOIN vpn_connections c ON u.user_id = c.user_id JOIN vpn_performance p ON c.connection_id = p.connection_id;

SELECT u.username, SUM(d.data_transferred) AS total_data FROM vpn_users u JOIN vpn_connections c ON u.user_id = c.user_id JOIN vpn_usage d ON c.connection_id = d.connection_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING total_data > 1000;
